author: Cory Gardner
title: Sen. Cory Gardner: Coronavirus spread because of Chinese Communist Party’s ineptitude and deceptions
description: The more we learn about COVID-19 and its origins, the clearer it becomes that much of the death and suffering could have been avoided had the Chinese Communist Party taken this threat more seriously.
